Items.Title: Build It Plugin Core
Items.Description:
Core module for Build It Plugin

Smarter NPCs

 - If they slip or fall out of bounds, they’ll teleport back safely
 - Navigation on rough terrain, like stairs and uneven ground, is smoother than ever
